</th>
<th rowspan="2">
<p class="smc">Verh&#228;ltni&#223; des<br />
Mehrwerths zum<br />
Gesammtkapital</p>
</th>
</tr>

<tr valign="bottom">
<td>
<p class="smc"><small>Mk.</small></p>
</td>
<td>
<p class="smc"><small>Mk.</small></p>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>
<p class="smc">A</p>
</td>
<td>
